{% trans_default_domain 'site' %}

<p class="text text-justify">
    Cookies are text files placed on your computer to help the website analyze how users use the site. The data generated by cookies about your use of the site (including your IP address, which will be truncated) will be transmitted to and stored on our servers. We will use this information to evaluate your use of the site, compile reports on site activity for our own use, and provide other services related to site activity and Internet usage.
</p>
<p class="text text-justify">
    We may disclose this data to third parties in case of a legal obligation. We will not cross-reference your IP address with any other data we hold. By using this website, you expressly consent to the processing of your personal data by us under the conditions and for the purposes described above.
</p>
<p class="text text-justify">
    You can disable the use of cookies by selecting the appropriate settings in your browser. <strong>However, such deactivation may prevent the use of certain features of this website.</strong>
</p>
<p class="text text-justify">
    For more information, and if you have any doubt or need clarification, please contact us.
</p>
<p class="text text-justify">
    For further information about what French law says: <a href="http://www.cnil.fr/vos-obligations/sites-web-cookies-et-autres-traceurs/que-dit-la-loi">http://www.cnil.fr/vos-obligations/sites-web-cookies-et-autres-traceurs/que-dit-la-loi</a>
</p>

